4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge in the field. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum of 16 participants per class. Students will gain crucial skills in Windows, Linux, network and server administration, along with advanced topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence.

Upon completion, participants receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, acknowledged by various institutions. The course materials are available in English and Spanish, catering to a diverse audience. For more detailed information, please visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop